title: Winning numbers drawn in 'MultiMatch' game
maintext:
BALTIMORE (AP) _ The winning numbers in Thursday evening’s drawing of the Maryland Lottery’s “MultiMatch” game were:
03-13-16-24-29-34
(three, thirteen, sixteen, twenty-four, twenty-nine, thirty-four)
